data.name: Hero Counterattack
data.desc: When an "Elemental HERO" monster you control is destroyed by battle: Your opponent chooses and reveals 1 random card from your hand, then, if it is an "Elemental HERO" monster, you destroy 1 monster your opponent controls and Special Summon the chosen monster.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 2: The Duel Academy Years Mega Pack
